<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Feeling" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Feeling,</orth> subst. 1) the sense of touch: <bibl n="shak. son 141.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 141, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.337" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 337</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.625" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 625</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 2, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.1.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 1, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 78</bibl>. <cit><quote>the sense of f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 439" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 439</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) sensation, perception: <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3.301" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 301</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.4.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 4, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.68" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 68</bibl>. With <cit><quote>of:</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1578" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1578</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 1.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 2, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.3.141" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 3, 141</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 5.1.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 1, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.287" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 287</bibl>.
<lb />3) experience, knowledge: <cit><quote>he had some f. of the sport,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 127</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thou hast no f. of it,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 3.115" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 115</bibl></cit>.
<lb />4) sensibility: <bibl n="shak. luc 1317" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1317</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.2.30" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 2, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 2, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.257" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 257</bibl>.
